posting_body: ['Bay Court at Harbour Pointe', '11108 Chennault Beach Road, Mukilteo, WA, 98275', 'Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'x 105', 'OR Text', '105', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to contact our leasing team.', 'Use the link below for more details:', '<URL>', 'The Bay Court at Harbour Pointe Apartment Homes', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 720 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'From convenience to luxury we have everything you are looking for at Bay Court at Harbour Pointe in Mukilteo, WA.', 'Conveniently located in the heart of the Harbour Pointe, you will have dining, shopping and entertainment options around every corner.', 'We offer the best apartment living in Mukilteo, and with one, two and three bedroom options we are sure to have the perfect floor plan to fit your lifestyle.', "We'd love to welcome you home, come see the lifestyle we have to offer at Bay Court at Harbor Pointe.", 'Pet Policy', 'We welcome your furry friends!', 'Breed restrictions apply and max of 2 pets per apartment home.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday – 10AM – 6PM', 'Tuesday – 10AM – 7PM', 'Wednesday – Saturday – 10AM – 6PM', 'Sunday – 11AM – 6PM', 'We do not accept Comprehensive Reusable Tenant Screening Reports as defined by and pursuant to RCW 59.18.', 'Mukilteo apartments Bay Court at Harbour Pointe', 'ZSrJgB0jKEfx']
